<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Workspace Deletion Initiation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        p {
            color: #555;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .info-box p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #999;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://github.com/umar-phaedra/assets/blob/main/logo-icon-restat.png?raw=true"
                alt="Restat Logo" />
            <h1>Workspace Deletion Initiated for {{workspaceName}}</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>This is to confirm that a deletion request has been initiated for the workspace <b>{{workspaceName}}</b>.
            </p>
            <div class="info-box">
                <p>Initiation Date: <b>{{initiationDate}}</b></p>
                <p>Scheduled Deletion Date: <b>{{scheduledDeletionDate}}</b></p>
            </div>
            <p>The workspace and all its associated data will be permanently deleted on the scheduled deletion date
                above. If you wish to cancel this deletion or need more time to back up your data, please contact our
                support team before the deletion date.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this deletion, please contact us immediately to prevent any data loss.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your attention,</p>
            <p>The Restat Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; {{currentYear}} Restat. All rights reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>